show.description: Betrayed by his sworn brother, Ajay — a fallen martial artist with no memory — rises from the streets to reclaim his true identity as the rightful leader. In a world of deadly rivalries, he along with Emma and Mr. Roy fight to restore honor against the corrupt forces led by a wicked duo.
